[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":306},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2019\u002F05\u002F15\u002Fhexo-app-like-push-notifications\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2019\u002F05\u002F15\u002Fhexo-app-like-push-notifications\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2019\u002F05\u002F15\u002Fhexo-app-like-push-notifications\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2019\u002F05\u002F15\u002Fhexo-app-like-push-notifications\u002F":283,"related:\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2019\u002F05\u002F15\u002Fhexo-app-like-push-notifications\u002F":292},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20190515\u002F3137769270\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":268,"date":269,"description":19,"extension":270,"lang":271,"meta":272,"navigation":273,"path":274,"readingMinutes":275,"seo":276,"standalone":277,"stem":278,"tags":279,"tldr":280,"updated":269,"url":281,"__hash__":282},"content\u002Fen\u002FHexo\u002Fhexo-app-like-push-notifications.md","Adding App-Like Push Notifications to Hexo","7296773130",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":255},"minimark",[11,16,20,24,29,39,43,48,52,63,70,73,78,81,86,89,94,106,111,129,134,137,142,145,150,153,157,160,165,168,173,176,181,184,189,192,195,200,203,208,212,215,220,223,226,231,234,239,242,247,250],[12,13,15],"h2",{"id":14},"intro","Intro",[17,18,19],"p",{},"Most blogs want to notify readers when new posts go up. Usually you'd use RSS, but with mobile usage being what it is now, we'll take a different approach.",[12,21,23],{"id":22},"environment-for-this-post","Environment for this post",[25,26,28],"h3",{"id":27},"hexo-version","Hexo version",[30,31,32,36],"ul",{},[33,34,35],"li",{},"hexo: 3.8.0",[33,37,38],{},"hexo-cli: 2.0.0",[25,40,42],{"id":41},"next-version","NexT version",[30,44,45],{},[33,46,47],{},"NexT: 7.1.0",[12,49,51],{"id":50},"add-izooto-to-hexo","Add iZooto to Hexo",[17,53,54,55,62],{},"Head to ",[56,57,61],"a",{"href":58,"rel":59},"https:\u002F\u002Fpanel.izooto.com\u002Flogin",[60],"nofollow","iZooto"," and register \u002F log in.",[17,64,65],{},[66,67],"img",{"alt":68,"src":69},"Image","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002F2dk3Hrs.png",[17,71,72],{},"Since I'd already used iZooto before, I'll skip ahead to adding a site. Click \"Add Website\" at the top:",[17,74,75],{},[66,76],{"alt":68,"src":77},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FXhqqEnd.png",[17,79,80],{},"A dialog will pop up — fill in the fields to generate the code (just need URL and site title):",[17,82,83],{},[66,84],{"alt":68,"src":85},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FJTqDHFD.png",[17,87,88],{},"After submitting, you'll get a code snippet. Copy it.",[17,90,91],{},[66,92],{"alt":68,"src":93},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FAG4pKiB.png",[17,95,96,97,101,102,105],{},"Step 1: drop the contents of the downloaded ",[98,99,100],"code",{},"izooto-sdk"," into the system root ",[98,103,104],{},"source"," folder.",[17,107,108],{},[66,109],{"alt":68,"src":110},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FvIaGe1D.png",[17,112,113,114,117,118,121,122,125,126,128],{},"Step 2: modify the Hexo template. Paste the snippet from earlier into ",[98,115,116],{},"\u003Chead>",". Find the theme's ",[98,119,120],{},"head.swig"," (",[98,123,124],{},"theme\u002Flayout\u002F_partials\u002Fhead\u002Fhead.swig",") and paste it there. Anywhere inside ",[98,127,120],{}," should work — just before line 130. If you're unsure, just put it where I did.",[17,130,131],{},[66,132],{"alt":68,"src":133},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FZQCjXTP.png",[17,135,136],{},"To verify it's working, open DevTools (F12) and look for it:",[17,138,139],{},[66,140],{"alt":68,"src":141},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002F9CfK1s6.png",[17,143,144],{},"Once it's looking good, push your Hexo and open it in another browser. If you see this dialog, it's working:",[17,146,147],{},[66,148],{"alt":68,"src":149},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FrhY6i2O.png",[17,151,152],{},"Note: both steps are required — miss one and it won't work.",[12,154,156],{"id":155},"izooto-dashboard","iZooto dashboard",[17,158,159],{},"The dashboard lets you tweak the subscription dialog style.",[17,161,162],{},[66,163],{"alt":68,"src":164},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002F1gWFXxU.png",[17,166,167],{},"I'm using this style:",[17,169,170],{},[66,171],{"alt":68,"src":172},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FKeiuCVo.png",[17,174,175],{},"Mobile subscription dialog can also be customised:",[17,177,178],{},[66,179],{"alt":68,"src":180},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002Fv9SJUh3.png",[17,182,183],{},"For the re-prompt timing (after a user clicks \"later\"), I'd recommend leaving the default (1 hour).",[17,185,186],{},[66,187],{"alt":68,"src":188},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FALwfCKx.png",[17,190,191],{},"After updating, give it a bit and you'll see your site's subscription dialog change.",[17,193,194],{},"PC:",[17,196,197],{},[66,198],{"alt":68,"src":199},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002F6h99qs9.png",[17,201,202],{},"Mobile:",[17,204,205],{},[66,206],{"alt":68,"src":207},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FvdElkem.png",[12,209,211],{"id":210},"sending-push-notifications","Sending push notifications",[17,213,214],{},"Sending is easy — click \"Create Campaign\" to open the send screen.",[17,216,217],{},[66,218],{"alt":68,"src":219},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002F5hvTtnD.png",[17,221,222],{},"Fill in the fields and send.",[17,224,225],{},"The one key field is \"Landing URL\" — the page that opens when a user clicks the notification.",[17,227,228],{},[66,229],{"alt":68,"src":230},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FQPgU7Rm.png",[17,232,233],{},"Adjust everything else to your needs, then scroll down to send.",[17,235,236],{},[66,237],{"alt":68,"src":238},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FgRwjJlw.png",[17,240,241],{},"After clicking send, it asks for confirmation:",[17,243,244],{},[66,245],{"alt":68,"src":246},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FMG6QU4M.png",[17,248,249],{},"After sending, you'll get the notification on your desktop.",[17,251,252],{},[66,253],{"alt":68,"src":254},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FmzpVl25.png",{"title":256,"searchDepth":257,"depth":257,"links":258},"",2,[259,260,265,266,267],{"id":14,"depth":257,"text":15},{"id":22,"depth":257,"text":23,"children":261},[262,264],{"id":27,"depth":263,"text":28},3,{"id":41,"depth":263,"text":42},{"id":50,"depth":257,"text":51},{"id":155,"depth":257,"text":156},{"id":210,"depth":257,"text":211},"Hexo","2019-05-15 13:58:15","md","en",{},true,"\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002Fhexo-app-like-push-notifications","2",{"title":6,"description":19},false,"en\u002FHexo\u002Fhexo-app-like-push-notifications",[268,61],null,"\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2019\u002F05\u002F15\u002Fhexo-app-like-push-notifications\u002F","kDwR267zxZTZ-wrCQeeG6PIh32gOW0xE0kyj-Ahqooc",{"newer":284,"older":288},{"url":285,"title":286,"date":287},"\u002Fen\u002Fjsweirdworld\u002F2019\u002F05\u002F15\u002Fjs-weird-world-05-undefined-vs-not-defined\u002F","[JS Weird World] No.5 A Quick Reminder: JavaScript and Undefined","2019-05-15 21:00:35",{"url":289,"title":290,"date":291},"\u002Fen\u002Fjsweirdworld\u002F2019\u002F05\u002F15\u002Fjs-weird-world-04-creation-and-hoisting\u002F","[JS Weird World] No.4 The Execution Context: Creation and Hoisting","2019-05-15 12:00:35",[293,297,302],{"url":294,"title":295,"date":296,"readingMinutes":275},"\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2022\u002F10\u002F30\u002Ffix-hexo-updated-date-on-ci-deploy\u002F","Fix: All Posts Show Updated Date After Hexo Upgrade or CI Deploy","2022-10-30 11:52:35",{"url":298,"title":299,"date":300,"readingMinutes":301},"\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F11\u002F01\u002Flearn-hexo-33-updating-next-theme\u002F","(33) Learning Hexo from Scratch - Extras: Updating the NexT Theme","2020-11-01 13:21:00","3",{"url":303,"title":304,"date":305,"readingMinutes":275},"\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F10\u002F31\u002Flearn-hexo-32-updating-hexo\u002F","(32) Learning Hexo from Scratch - Extras: Updating Hexo","2020-10-31 14:01:51",1784087326157]